**Summary:** Ampli is a code generation tool that creates type-safe wrappers for Amplitude SDK based on tracking plans defined in Amplitude Data, providing compile-time validation, autocompletion, and instrumentation verification through the Ampli CLI.

**Keywords:**
- Ampli wrapper generation
- Amplitude Data tracking plan
- Ampli CLI commands (pull, status, configure)
- Type-safe event tracking
- Compile-time validation
- Event instrumentation verification
- Source code scanning
- SDK wrapper facade
- Analytics tracking plan
- Event property validation
- TypeScript autocompletion
- ampli.load() configuration
- ampli.songPlayed() methods
- Static type checks
- Data quality enforcement